<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="hook-v">hook <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /hʊk/    美 /hʊk/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-vt-vi">1.★ <strong>vt &amp; vi (被) 钩住；引 (人) 上钩；钓 (鱼)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The unlucky fisherman hooked an old shoe.
这个渔夫很不走运，钓起了一只旧鞋。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>hooked /hʊkt/ adj [不用于名词前]  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They are <strong>hooked on</strong> shopping and usually buy things that they don't need.
她们购物成瘾，往往买些自己不需要的东西。</p><footer>2008 山东</footer></div></div>